    q: "How long does an outdoor sauna last?",
    a: "With a good foundation and basic upkeep, a well-built outdoor sauna lasts 10-20+ years. The biggest factors are wood quality (thermowood and clear cedar resist rot and warping best), a level well-drained base that keeps the structure off wet ground, and yearly maintenance like re-oiling exterior wood and checking the heater. Skimp on the foundation and the door seals and frame fail far sooner.",
